          "summary": "使用多項式雜湊（單模/雙模）快速比較子串。適用於子串匹配、重複子串、最長公共子串等。推薦先做 2156. 查詢給定雜湊值的子串。可二分比較字典序。\n\n**C++ 模板**：\n\n```cpp\n// 字串雜湊（多項式雜湊）\nstruct StringHash {\n    static const long long MOD = 1e9 + 7, BASE = 131;\n    vector<long long> h, pw;\n    StringHash(const string& s) {\n        int n = s.size();\n        h.resize(n + 1);\n        pw.resize(n + 1);\n        h[0] = 0;\n        pw[0] = 1;\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n            h[i + 1] = (h[i] * BASE + s[i]) % MOD;\n            pw[i + 1] = pw[i] * BASE % MOD;\n        }\n    }\n    long long get(int l, int r) {\n        return (h[r + 1] - h[l] * pw[r - l + 1] % MOD + MOD * 2) % MOD;\n    }\n};\n```"
